1. compile IDL

	idlj -fall Relay.idl

2. Compile all stubs and skeletons

	javac *.java ClientAndServer/*.java

Instructions to run the Home security system

First run the regional office

Second run home hub, give name and set contact number for messages

Third run camera/sensor, give both name, the existing hub name and rooms (different rooms)

Features:

Send panic
Send okay
See status
Request image
Switch on/off
Assign rooms - 2 rooms, one camera or sensor, sensor and sensor, camera and camera to set of alarm
Check camera status
Reset Alarm
View camera/sensor logs
Save logs to text file
View home hub logs
Send user text message




